Every cycle you will be assigned to a player. If your player goes to tribal you will also go to tribal here. You can then vote for your fellow tribe mates but who you vote for will get a "rock" we will then run rocks of these votes to see who falls to fate and goes home. (basically one rock will be chosen and that person will go home) REMEMBER I CAN ANY BITS AT ANY TIME IF THEY ARE FUNNY ENOUGH. To sign up say the player you want to start out as, (you will randomly get a new one every cycle) If your player was already picked just pick a new one. ANY PLAYERS WHO PLAYED LAST SEASONS ROCK GAME MAY NOT SIGN UP UNTILL LATER. Happy rocking I will ping eventually lol
